 where the mean free path is 0.1 times the radius. In\nthree spatial dimensions, the convective motions make it difficult to predict\nwhere this happens and to possibly improve the closure relation there.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 5 Apr 2020 04:30:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 31 Aug 2020 07:01:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-11"}
